<opener><salute>Illustrissimo atque Celeberrimo 
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>P.</abbr><expan>Petrus</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>A.</abbr><expan>Antonius</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>In hanc <rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentoratensium</rs> Urbem protinus ut veni Nobilissimus Vene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>torum Legatus <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person"><choice><abbr>Laur.</abbr><expan>Laurentius</expan></choice> Theupolus</rs> Eques, ac <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> Marci <choice><abbr>Procu.<hi rend="#sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Procurator</expan></choice> cubiti, dexter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
             <lb/>manus, dextrique <choice><sic>genu</sic><corr>genus</corr></choice> dolore ita conflictari coepit, ut hanc vestram
             <lb/>inclytam accedendi Civitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice><!-- orttag -->, Te potissimum, Vir Amicissime, salutandi
             <lb/>atque videndi causa, voluptate privari fuerim coactus. Quoniam
             <lb/>igitur fato, nescio quo, Te osculandi, Tibique meam erga Te gratitudi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nem coram testificandi occasio veluti mihi abripitur, quod orete<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare nequeo per litteras efficere conabor, donec aliud
             <lb/>ad vos veniendi peropportun<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tempus adveniat. Statim ac
             <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person"><choice><abbr>Excellentiss.<hi rend="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimus</expan></choice> Vir</rs> modo memoratus convalescet primum <rs key="place_GEO-2954172" type="place">Augustam
                <lb/>Vindelicor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, inde <rs key="place_GEO-3165243" type="place">Trident<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, postea <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> maximis itineribus
             <lb/>contendemus, quo ubi pervenero tuas <rs key="B_1722-08-12_991170515149205501" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Kontrollieren: Der letzte Brief 000056719 von Joh. I B. an Michelotti datiert vom 12. August 1722.</note> mihi pergratas
             <lb/>atque <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me diu optatas expectabo. Maximo me favore afficies,
             <lb/>Vir sapientissime, si aliquando cogitabis de ratione solvendi, diluen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dique <choice><abbr>Illustriss.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person"><choice><abbr>Jacob.</abbr><expan>Jacobi</expan></choice> Riccati</rs> objectiones,<note type="editorial">Riccati-Kontroverse</note> seu difficultates, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tereaque
             <lb/>ad me perscribes quid Tibi videatur de illusmodi objectionibus militantibus pro
             <lb/><rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">corollario</rs><note type="editorial">werktag: newtonbhbd für die 1713er-Ausgabe der Principia schon eingesetzt, ABER: Hier wird spezifisch auf das 2. Corrolar verwiesen. Wäre das auszuweisen? Bibliogr. Angabe: Newton, Isaac, Philosophiae naturalis principia mathematica. Editio secunda auctior et emendatior, Cantabrigiae [Cambridge] (C. Crownfield) 1713. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> newtoniano pertinente ad vim,<note type="editorial">Newton Principia 1687, Liber 2, Prop. XXXVII, Prob. IX, pag. 330 und Newton Principia 1713, Corol. 2 von Prop. XXXVI, Probl. VIII (p. 307).</note> totum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen
             <lb/>in fundo vasis factum exilientis mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, generant<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>. Etenim, aiebat
             <lb/>ipse <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>, quoniam effectus dato tempore geniti sunt suis ad<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatis
             <lb/>causis proportionales, et effectus dato tempore generatus, in <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ni</rs> casu, sit quantitas aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis duplo column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><sic>acque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice> pro
             <lb/>base foramen in fundo fact<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, pro altitudine ipsius vasis altitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>din<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> habentis, consequens est, vim totum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> effluentis motum
             <lb/>producentem <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qual<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> esse duplo, non simplici ponderi <choice><sic>acque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice>
<lb/>column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> modo commemorat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, eam ni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mirum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> mihi communicasti pro demonstrando vim, requi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>sit<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ad generand<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> motum esse <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qual<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> simplici pon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>deri dict<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><sic>acque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, paralogismo laborare asseruit i<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dem <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>; qui concedit quid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> antequam foramen in fundo vasis
             <lb/>fiat, ipsum foramen sustinere, ideoque premi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> simplici pon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dere column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><sic>acque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice> s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>p<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> memorat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vasis foramini ad perpen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>diculum insistentis; at ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> negat fact<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> jam apertura in ipso
             <pb facs="1079336" n="2"/>
<lb/>vasis fundo, vim generantem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> motum totam, quanta est, attribuen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dam esse simplici <choice><sic>acque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> foramini insistentis pon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>deri. Ego puto responderi posse, agi in casu nostro de vi ge<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nerante primum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exilientis mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> tempusculo indefini<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>te parvo, non aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> de vi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> requiritur ad efficiend<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ut certo
             <lb/>tempore finito exiliat certa aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quantitas definita. Ver<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>ambigo an huiusmodi responsio sufficiat ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatian<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> diffi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cultat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tollend<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>. Putat demum (secus ac Tu, Vir Doctissime exis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>timas) comparari posse vim acceleratricem cum vi gravitatis, in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>deque null<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> nasci absurditat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> sibi persuadet, propterea quod ejusmodi compara<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tiones non sunt nisi relationes qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c Tibi, et fortasse cum
             <lb/>tedio repeto, verens ne forte [non?] servaris longissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
             <lb/><rs key="B_1722-01-23_991170515149605501" type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Der Brief 000056715 vom 23. Januar 1722 ist der einzige Brief, den Michelotti an Joh. I B. im Januar diesen Jahres schreibt.</note>,
                <lb/>quam jam pridem, nimirum Januario jam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito raptim ad
                <lb/>Te scriptitavi, et ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> nunqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> adversa pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>peditus valetudine
                <lb/>respondere valuisti. Si possum Te etiam atque etiam orare, Vir
                <lb/>Ingeniosissime, Te qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, et obsecro, ut epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice><!-- brieftag --><note type="editorial">Ist dieser Brief auch referenzierbar?</note> ad me scribas om<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dici possunt de s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pius commemorato corollario<rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio"/><note type="editorial">werktag: newtonbhbd für die 1713er-Ausgabe der Principia schon eingesetzt, ABER: Hier wird spezifisch auf das 2. Corrolar verwiesen. Wäre das auszuweisen? Bibliogr. Angabe: Newton, Isaac, Philosophiae naturalis principia mathematica. Editio secunda auctior et emendatior, Cantabrigiae [Cambridge] (C. Crownfield) 1713. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonia<unclear>n</unclear>o</rs>
<lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tereaque de <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatianis</rs> objectionibus complectentem.<note type="editorial">Riccati-Kontroverse</note> Hoc si
                <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te impetraro, me Tibi pluribus de nominibus jam obstrictum,
                <lb/>quammaxime devinct<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> putabo. Hac in <rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Urbe</rs><note type="editorial">Strasbourg</note> permanebo (nam
                <lb/>Amplissimus Legatus <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolus</rs> hodi<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> maxime torquetur manus,
